abstract: Walgreen reports fiscal first-quarter earnings $809 million, increase of 16 percent from year earlier; revenue rose nearly 7 percent to $19.55 billion; results surpass analyst expectations.
lead_paragraph: Walgreen earned $809 million, a 16 percent increase from last year’s total of $695 million.
